Sunhawk was blasted through the wall.  From the rubble
he held up his hands to utter a few last words.

Sunhawk:  Snowowl....I will soon be with........you.

He hand drops as he goes offline.  Rather than joining
with the Matrix a mysterious force takes control of
his spark lifting it to far above the Earth.

OOC: I'm taking control of a Vok faction for my own
purposes.
